  "focus_spans": [
    {
      "end_byte": 121,
      "focus_id": "F001",
      "source_text": "本文档不是实验流水账，而是给论文写作使用的",
      "source_text_sha256": "24977837b88b3290d1bfb0b663fd87f170efc29c6ff389e3da816af32437dd95",
      "start_byte": 58
    },
    {
      "end_byte": 181,
      "focus_id": "F002",
      "source_text": "。它专门回答六个问题：",
      "source_text_sha256": "6d023e1a84df90a9a10be13ceecb10e289090df51c701b40a79e1dca75115290",
      "start_byte": 148
    },
    {
      "end_byte": 231,
      "focus_id": "F003",
      "source_text": "我们现在最强的主张到底是什么。",
      "source_text_sha256": "90d585464533ce7aa8532e45b02ad8fa5d4407f2b3b02d551ec84520f24dbf38",
      "start_byte": 186
    },
    {
      "end_byte": 289,
      "focus_id": "F004",
      "source_text": "哪些结果已经足够进入论文主表与主图。",
      "source_text_sha256": "efce1ff559e21060af547badcc7d3fe199608ca68ec002edf9a3125e4f080102",
      "start_byte": 235
    },
    {
      "end_byte": 353,
      "focus_id": "F005",
      "source_text": "哪些结果只能作为第二梯队支持或边界条件。",
      "source_text_sha256": "288a192a13ad6d62812adcf0da5cac1ac822e2a4114c6a95c7a8441c6283b146",
      "start_byte": 293
    },
    {
      "end_byte": 434,
      "focus_id": "F006",
      "source_text": "到底证明了什么、没证明什么。",
      "source_text_sha256": "2f75cd51c710c98caca2cc93f23bbb8016aeda35736ce105ef7b6fc88f2b5dc3",
      "start_byte": 392
    },
    {
      "end_byte": 492,
      "focus_id": "F007",
      "source_text": "审稿人可能怎么质疑，我们该如何回应。",
      "source_text_sha256": "0ca965c5e73b4afeac3f2c83c369d8ea0a8367e090579a67f7f87a609ac5bfd6",
      "start_byte": 438
    },
    {
      "end_byte": 558,
      "focus_id": "F008",
      "source_text": "论文 Results/Discussion 现在最合理的写法是什么。",
      "source_text_sha256": "c0b278bcceace46447e4dff3427ad35a6e03bf815376bcd680661b22d933855e",
      "start_byte": 496
    },
    {
      "end_byte": 666,
      "focus_id": "F009",
      "source_text": "当前数据支持一个分层、谨慎但已经相当有力的主张：",
      "source_text_sha256": "581c90138b5a25c5333381755655b64b8e87dc87cbd2091184eb2df723dc2d89",
      "start_byte": 594
    },
    {
      "end_byte": 1051,
      "focus_id": "F010",
      "source_text": "更进一步，在 ",
      "source_text_sha256": "8c8d48b900e5975afbf458803ecc5bff9f59cf7c4f48e07482605a0e7f8ba2ba",
      "start_byte": 1032
    },
    {
      "end_byte": 1131,
      "focus_id": "F011",
      "source_text": " 的独立预算 method-line 实验里，我们已经看到：",
      "source_text_sha256": "70a2c55daa6cc5d07f54185907a35d9d61a32a794c29f6ecb6f17c24af177494",
      "start_byte": 1069
    },
    {
      "end_byte": 1397,
      "focus_id": "F012",
      "source_text": "purity 很低、但 geometry-first 的便宜分解器",
      "source_text_sha256": "21aca7ea2c9528a2eedd2ccc6cdea680f3208e65e9e6a40e7103e70a1adcf9ef",
      "start_byte": 1344
    },
    {
      "end_byte": 1441,
      "focus_id": "F013",
      "source_text": "更谨慎地说，这仍然不是一个",
      "source_text_sha256": "001637b6ec9005910cdf754bfa7019ebe76c0be39a09a6a37b06811ad9ff52fd",
      "start_byte": 1402
    },
    {
      "end_byte": 1536,
      "focus_id": "F014",
      "source_text": "的万能定理。",
      "source_text_sha256": "165a501bc8e47b1b7052ab9eb298ca1df398ccdd6d57582a56e6af4ef647b2f7",
      "start_byte": 1518
    },
    {
      "end_byte": 1751,
      "focus_id": "F015",
      "source_text": "因此论文必须采用",
      "source_text_sha256": "80e807832da7caafa87677cede83762a7bb17159ee98c48c5acbbb17d17bde16",
      "start_byte": 1727
    },
    {
      "end_byte": 1820,
      "focus_id": "F016",
      "source_text": "的叙事，而不是一刀切。",
      "source_text_sha256": "d9dd36004f3e09aaf4a94461a3d544dbbb215ef2eddd82afabaadb66badd6003",
      "start_byte": 1787
    },
    {
      "end_byte": 1900,
      "focus_id": "F017",
      "source_text": "### 2.1 强证据：可以进入论文主结果",
      "source_text_sha256": "0fbddeebe91ceda87a132965d431f4e270a5fb8cd7faafe2bd7310e98d883157",
      "start_byte": 1853
    },
    {
      "end_byte": 4274,
      "focus_id": "F018",
      "source_text": "**Method-line 的 independent paper 已经足够进入一个单独 Results 小节。**",
      "source_text_sha256": "1ae849578132bdaf2c3769c7adf025d06307779d1c850846ddb228bf1526fe89",
      "start_byte": 4188
    },
    {
      "end_byte": 5209,
      "focus_id": "F019",
      "source_text": "### 2.2 中等证据：可以作为第二梯队支持",
      "source_text_sha256": "dafa31eb6256c84487e480b4d62d07ab5b919f5294541d55d55620c4b00a0238",
      "start_byte": 5156
    },
    {
      "end_byte": 6010,
      "focus_id": "F020",
      "source_text": "不过这些函数的收敛过程更复杂，不能只看单一指标。",
      "source_text_sha256": "b106a20f504badf22d0db64432df71f82ecb0571d2e74f8cad9c0ece22df6962",
      "start_byte": 5938
    },
    {
      "end_byte": 6100,
      "focus_id": "F021",
      "source_text": "**证据链派生表和图已经足以把几何、性能、统计归因连起来。**",
      "source_text_sha256": "2dd974fb83b6fb7f511fdf29e3b5997ff4d6c1390bdb5783e0950b8b90c58dd5",
      "start_byte": 6015
    },
    {
      "end_byte": 6124,
      "focus_id": "F022",
      "source_text": "主线 analysis：",
      "source_text_sha256": "5d35b6a1dc8dc9d03a90ad7e6b71cb14fdbdc121e1fd722a1594c8fb25f15c15",
      "start_byte": 6106
    },
    {
      "end_byte": 6209,
      "focus_id": "F023",
      "source_text": "主线图：",
      "source_text_sha256": "51649b74c9eaa3571f39f518ee0a121c29ac0155225d8ef4ed8771b69002243a",
      "start_byte": 6197
    }
  ],
